{"tid":1845715,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【沙盤推演】醫護罷工危機，柒婆如何不敗","createTime":"2020-01-27T10:05:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T08:26:37.000Z","uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5e3d3ca5caa0c6b57b467d301df4929331a2d32f","tid":1845715,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T10:05:20.000Z","msg":"中國武漢肺炎喺香港大爆發已經難以避免，而醫護大罷工將係情勢發展關鍵。估計柒婆嘅如意算盤係，無論罷工搞唔搞得成，自己都立於不敗之地。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">A&bull; 罷工失敗，歸功於官員領導有方，帶領醫療界同心協力，接收大批北方病人。<br />\n<br />\nB&bull; 醫護大罷工，醫療頻臨崩潰。柒婆用緊急法引入「境外」醫護化解危機，成功推動大灣區醫療融合。<br />\n</span><br />\n暫時連登未有討論到呢一步，但其實快則半個月內就會發生。各位智囊點拆好？"},{"pid":"13618b3afd6823d4fa1e25aff68085360aec5de2","tid":1845715,"uid":194326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T10:09:14.000Z","msg":"system 唔同點引入？"},{"pid":"6fc62884b895f2d939c8500d6977a5cac686ace3","tid":1845715,"uid":260639,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T10:52:24.000Z","msg":"如果有咁簡單就好<br />\n香港個醫療系統好覆雜<br />\n外國醫生入到黎都暈<br />\n除非成個醫療系統推倒重造<br />\n同埋放棄國際醫療界認證<br />\n香港考牌照(醫生護士抽血員醫療化驗etc )<br />\n大部分係國際通用<br />\n大陸無呢種認證<br />\n你叫大陸人過黎，一係重新考牌，一係請&quot;無牌&quot;<br />\n香港又少一個重要支柱產業<br />\n到呢個地步就真。攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54d3943a7ff9ac18f1c71815422c6283f42d9c7f","tid":1845715,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13618b3afd6823d4fa1e25aff68085360aec5de2","tid":1845715,"uid":194326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T10:09:14.000Z","msg":"system 唔同點引入？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T06:07:16.000Z","msg":"話冇可能嘅人，點睇？<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AW4aORq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAW4aORq.png&h=55f67b38&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e84450f164992aa9f9e6e4e2b1d274dea11710cb","tid":1845715,"uid":15548,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T06:25:18.000Z","msg":"B實際點執行<br />\n唔係覺得而家大陸會有醫護放落黎掛？"},{"pid":"e2e5ab7df7acee1382eec3af36403d5bab8e5679","tid":1845715,"uid":276716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e84450f164992aa9f9e6e4e2b1d274dea11710cb","tid":1845715,"uid":15548,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T06:25:18.000Z","msg":"B實際點執行<br />\n唔係覺得而家大陸會有醫護放落黎掛？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:28:30.000Z","msg":"大把嘢玩啦<br />\n<br />\n方案A: 鑑於香港醫療瀕臨崩潰，又有上海團隊派往武漢的先例，特區政府致函國務院批准珠三角醫護團隊派駐香港。特首表示感謝國家對香港的支持。<br />\n<br />\n方案B: 香港醫院缺乏人手照顧病人，而肺炎病人由於傳染性高不宜轉移，醫管局決定將其他普通病人轉移至深圳醫院繼續治療。特首對深圳市政府表示感謝。<br />\n<br />\n方案C: 政府決定於河套區興建肺炎醫院，兩星期內落成。屆時由大灣區醫療團隊進駐，集中處理大灣區肺炎病人。特首對廣東省政府表示感謝。"},{"pid":"5fcde63912b0070c98956168cf04882e247ac4e4","tid":1845715,"uid":226955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:37:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">[事關重大請廣傳]</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人以及醫護、海關等要職唔一齊三罷嘅後果，只會鼓勵更多支那感染者衝嚟香港求醫，間接促成社區爆發，害死包括醫護同海關全家在內嘅更多人<br />\n<br />\n我會支持三罷，亦會身體力行一齊三罷保護香港，直至港府落實封關<br />\n<br />\n大家唔通想犧牲香港200萬手足同自己全家條命去救呢d準備落地獄嘅人渣？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「感染的人越多越好」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aMf1RYs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaMf1RYs.jpg&h=d189414d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">把我臉上的口罩撕下來朝我吐了口吐沫，說「我活不了，你們都別想活」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XkLMVDM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXkLMVDM.jpg&h=058fd92f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">撕扯她們的防護服<br />\n「要死一起死」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i7qtpw7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi7qtpw7.jpg&h=11a8b2cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"62b884c069b32156d5bf2063edfb7f2d0cd7e13f","tid":1845715,"uid":86833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:44:35.000Z","msg":"終国人會反對B先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n分分鐘暴動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e94ae9c4a69b0d8f65d08a3f1dcf23770129bedf","tid":1845715,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62b884c069b32156d5bf2063edfb7f2d0cd7e13f","tid":1845715,"uid":86833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:44:35.000Z","msg":"終国人會反對B先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n分分鐘暴動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T08:02:09.000Z","msg":"咩叫「杮子選軟的捏」？<br />\n你估佢哋會針對香港人定共產黨<br />\n<br />\n「既然醫生都派到香港，我們也一起到香港醫院去！」"},{"pid":"d8ffa1046af5eee7706b61ce42eaf78f43ac3744","tid":1845715,"uid":264009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T08:26:37.000Z","msg":"如何引入個唔知頭唔知路的外地醫護去本地病房做？B做唔倒的。"}]}